At the 2000 [[census]],<ref name="GR2" /> there were 49 people, 19 households and 14 families residing in the town. The population density was {{convert|255.5|PD/sqmi|PD/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. There were 23 housing units at an average density of {{convert|119.9|/sqmi|/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. The racial makeup of the town was 100.00% [[White (U.S. Census)|White]]. By the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 91 people residing in the town.

